text: Brinian is a village on the island of Rousay, in Orkney, Scotland. Trumland is situated to the west of the village, with Taversöe Tuick nearby. Brinian is within the parish of Rousay and Egilsay. ==References== ==External links== *Around Rousay - Brinian *GEN UKI - Brinian Kirkyard *The Megalithic Portal - Cubbie Roo's Burden *Undiscovered Scotland - Taversoe Tuick Cairn Category:Villages in Orkney
